                   on the Highway, taking from him 2 s. and 6 d. in Money
            </rs>, on the <rs id="t17270830-29-cd136" type="crimeDate">28th of May</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17270830-29-off134 t17270830-29-cd136"></join>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17270830-29-off138 t17270830-29-cd136"></join> last, being Sunday at Noon, in a common Road near <placeName id="t17270830-29-crimeloc137">Hackney</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17270830-29-crimeloc137" type="placeName" value="Hackney"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17270830-29-crimeloc137" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
